
install step:
1. git submodule init
2. git submodule update
3. ln ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
4. install ctags and cscope
5. install Clang_Complete

how to:
1. press F2 to toggle NerdTree
2. press F3 to toggle taglist
3. press F4 to toggle quickFix
4. press F7 to execute ":Grep" 
5. press F5 to execute ":make"
6. execute ":A" to switch between cpp file and h file
7. press F8 to generate ctags and cscope file in the root folder.

install Clang_Complete
1. apt-get install libclang1 and libclang-dev (clang?)
2. to the "Clang_Complete" plugin folder and type"make install"

generate ctags
1. ctags -R --c++-kinds=+p --fields=+iaS --extra=+q /usr/include
2. ctags -R *

